      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BROWNLOW (8) rocketed out of the boxes with a fast early split and gave a sight before being swamped late, finishing a 1.75 lengths fifth at this track over 520m in 30.39. Safe beginner but wide box to overcome and will need some luck. Has ability and can bounce back. LITTLE CLIFFY (2) last appeared when too good (17.99) over 300m at Taree Super Track on December 10. Resumes after finishing sixth (17.99) at Taree Super Track over 300m four months ago. Solid record at the distance winning four races. This looks easier and expected to run well. AKELA JUDO (3) hit the frame last time at this track but the start prior rocketed around 520m at this track in 29.81. Smart winner two back and looks a key chance on that form. ZIPPING ADELINE (1) is in the mix despite missing out at this track last time.",
